{"tid":987560,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"超級唔鍾意呢類人「有圖」","createTime":"2019-01-19T11:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T12:59:42.000Z","uid":227257,"like":16,"dislike":679,"uniUserReply":112,"replies":[{"pid":"26cfb741b941a9ddc652fe9276faa0ef31a9b9d6","tid":987560,"uid":227257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T11:55:54.000Z","msg":"是咁的，由於今日有個叔叔幫我地屋企整d木工既東西，母上為了答謝叔叔，請佢食飯，點知個叔叔超級唔客氣，又叫我母上買衫比佢，又唔客氣咁點菜。<br />\n好啦，上菜了，叔叔話咁快食曬d菜，我只能靠湯來拌飯⋯⋯個叔叔差不多一個人食曬d嘢「得談笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n我個人唔鍾意呢種人⋯點先可以唔比佢再來我屋企<br />\nPs，佢食煙，成身煙味，好燃臭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X2N6adj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX2N6adj.png&h=3c58d72d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AkpgxrS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAkpgxrS.png&h=a06817e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b76f69cde39ede180d1ce4966d8b058d118b5bf3","tid":987560,"uid":2300,"like":1189,"dislike":5,"score":1184,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T11:58:23.000Z","msg":"我今日真係好開心呀， 我諗聽日一定會更加開心既姐，係咪呀，哈姆太郎 ？"},{"pid":"bdd8d7486c446abde328cf57781f8df98cd6a1f1","tid":987560,"uid":45635,"like":331,"dislike":4,"score":327,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T11:58:59.000Z","msg":"成碗狗飯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6cef3f9e762901b6097e7740af08387c7e8c202","tid":987560,"uid":93649,"like":178,"dislike":0,"score":178,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T11:59:00.000Z","msg":"咁咪出邊搵師傅整囉"},{"pid":"411e14611456c5f22107909e49dd42cdcb13b7af","tid":987560,"uid":122139,"like":337,"dislike":1,"score":336,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T11:59:21.000Z","msg":"啲圖有=冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f286fd2fa354975